ji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"陳雲條on9仔吸能左甘勁既內功都唔能識運用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比王小虎禁住個頭黎小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當佢臭雞甘屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 韋陀條七頭幾時上到火雲邪神級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成能日屌打弱雞黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怕死多次啊廢人"},{"pid":"a4d231075d148ec8cef28824ff2dc190a9aeffc0","tid":526234,"uid":31585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"根本龍虎門個班淨係打得贏二打六<br />\n東方無敵同火雲邪神根本打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b59ef194a0ae07c6b6c238219c36c756a76947","tid":526234,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"復活係100%嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87ed1bcdb4e42d1bc3d81471d5835ea275bf6e4","tid":526234,"uid":82905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本龍虎門個班淨係打得贏二打六<br />\n東方無敵同火雲邪神根本打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每次出一大班2打6 跟本唔會記到名<br />\n而家出獵神者除左金神魔君同極樂魔曾呢兩隻中二名中boss認得之外 <br />\n重點係完全feel唔到獵神者到底有咩勁<br />\n除左天下無敵仲有一堆咁既蛋散<br />\n吸功講到咁勁比絕緣手套破左<br />\n<br />\n快撚d滅左龍虎門 <br />\n東方無敵同火雲邪神再死戰多次<br />\n<br />\n全滅大結局好過啦🤡"},{"pid":"4d3c61eb7537bb0380cc8566d1a529cab86a73ab","tid":526234,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"Owen Chan死左?<br />\n<br />\n好多年無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f72390bb40d1c724a2a840688099a55f26b27d8","tid":526234,"uid":51681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"呢d 煩膠角色唔好俾佢翻生⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"7ea52